---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { SITE } from "../../site-config";
---

<Layout
  title={`${SITE.author.fullName} - Projects - AI Research Assistant`}
  description="A multi-agent AI system built with LangGraph and Groq that autonomously researches any topic using real-time web search and generates a structured report. Features a Researcher, Analyst, and Writer agent working in a pipeline, served via a FastAPI backend and deployed on Hugging Face Spaces with Docker."
>
  <main class="w-full min-h-screen px-4 py-8 md:px-8 md:py-12 text-white max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <a
      href="/projects"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-100 bg-neutral-900 hover:bg-neutral-800 hover:border-neutral-500 w-fit px-4 py-2 border border-neutral-600 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200"
      >← Back</a
    >

    <div class="mt-10 mb-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-50 mb-3">
        AI Research Assistant
      </h1>
      <p class="text-neutral-300 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        A portfolio project focused on autonomous, structured research workflows.
        The system coordinates multiple AI roles to gather, validate, and synthesize
        information into a final report.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2 mb-8">
      <article class="group rounded-lg border border-darkslate-400 hover:border-neutral-500 bg-darkslate-500 p-6 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
          <div class="w-1 h-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-neutral-400 to-neutral-600 rounded-full"></div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-100">Project Overview</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
          This project uses a multi-agent architecture to break down complex
          research tasks into clear stages: exploration, analysis, and report
          writing.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="group rounded-lg border border-darkslate-400 hover:border-neutral-500 bg-darkslate-500 p-6 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
          <div class="w-1 h-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-neutral-400 to-neutral-600 rounded-full"></div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-100">Tech Stack</h2>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li class="text-neutral-300 flex items-center"><span class="mr-3">→</span> LangGraph, Groq API</li>
          <li class="text-neutral-300 flex items-center"><span class="mr-3">→</span> FastAPI backend</li>
          <li class="text-neutral-300 flex items-center"><span class="mr-3">→</span> Docker deployment</li>
          <li class="text-neutral-300 flex items-center"><span class="mr-3">→</span> Hugging Face Spaces</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-lg border border-darkslate-400 hover:border-neutral-500 bg-darkslate-500 p-6 mb-8 transition-all duration-300">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <div class="w-1 h-7 bg-gradient-to-b from-neutral-400 to-neutral-600 rounded-full"></div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-100">Key Features</h2>
      </div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 ml-3">
        <li class="text-neutral-300 flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-neutral-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">✓</span>
          <span>Automated topic decomposition and query planning</span>
        </li>
        <li class="text-neutral-300 flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-neutral-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">✓</span>
          <span>Evidence collection with source-based synthesis</span>
        </li>
        <li class="text-neutral-300 flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-neutral-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">✓</span>
          <span>Structured final report generation</span>
        </li>
        <li class="text-neutral-300 flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-neutral-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">✓</span>
          <span>Modular agent workflow for easy extension</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-lg border border-darkslate-400 hover:border-neutral-500 bg-darkslate-500 p-6 transition-all duration-300">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <div class="w-1 h-7 bg-gradient-to-b from-neutral-400 to-neutral-600 rounded-full"></div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-100">Project Links</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a
          href="https://hamza100x-ai-research-assistant.hf.space/ui"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="group/btn inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-neutral-900 hover:bg-neutral-800 hover:border-neutral-400 px-5 py-2.5 border border-neutral-600 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200"
        >
          <span>Live Demo</span>
          <span class="group-hover/btn:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-200">↗</span>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/hamza100x/ai-research-assistant"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="group/btn inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-neutral-900 hover:bg-neutral-800 hover:border-neutral-400 px-5 py-2.5 border border-neutral-600 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200"
        >
          <span>Source Code</span>
          <span class="group-hover/btn:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-200">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<script>
  // This page has no motion loader animation, so hide the global loader directly.
  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
    const loader = document.querySelector(".loader");
    if (loader) {
      loader.remove();
    }
  });
</script>
